<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Defs>

  <!--
  ============================ DECO door catalogue ============================
  Art reused from Doors Expanded (jecrell, MIT).

  1x1 doors  : vanilla Building_Door, pure XML.
  Multi-tile : DoorsExpanded.Building_DoorExpanded (Building_MultiTileDoor subclass) with a
               custom full-width slide draw, because the reused _Mover art is authored
               at full door width and vanilla's half-width two-leaf draw breaks it.

  Research folded into vanilla:
    - curtains, large doors : none (start of game)
    - jail door, gate       : Smithing
    - blast doors           : Machining
    - remote/garage doors   : Microelectronics  (M2 - not yet)
  -->

